 &lt;div class="comment" title="Comment: tangential aside"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Miller and Mazzucchelli also did 
&lt;a href="https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/daredevil-born-again-1986/"
 
 
 
 &gt;
 Daredevil: Born Again (1986)
 
&lt;/a&gt;
 together.&lt;/p&gt;
